where 
* formula_7 is the set of continuously differentiable vector functions of compact support contained in formula_8, 
* formula_9 is the essential supremum norm, and 
* formula_10 is the divergence operator. 
This definition &quot;does not require&quot; that the domain formula_11 of the given function be a bounded set.

