=== Translations ===

Mary Daly&#x27;s book, &quot;The Church and the Second Sex,&quot; was translated by Helen Hye-Sook Hwang in Korean and published by Women&#x27;s News Press in 1997.

Mary Daly&#x27;s book, &quot;Beyond God the Father: Toward a Philosophy of Women&#x27;s Liberation,&quot; was translated by Helen Hye-Sook Hwang in Korea and published by Ewha Women&#x27;s University in 1996.

